dct_title_s: Barnett's street plan of Gravesend & adjoining district.
dct_description_sm: G. I. Barnett & Son. With "Index to streets and places of interest". Based upon the Ordnance Survey map with the sanction of the Controller H. M. Stationery Office. Verso: London underground; Gravesend and surrounding districts; Barnett's map of Kent & E.Sussex.; two radius distance maps; Gravesen information.
